#Using fmap

## Prepare Kernel
```bash
sudo awk -F\' '$1=="menuentry " {print $2}' /etc/grub2.cf
sudo grub2-set-default 4
sudo reboot
```

## Prepare Fmap

### Set Memory for Fmap
```bash
vim driver/main.c
```
Gia na elegxeis posh mnhmh tha desmefsei h fmap kaneis

vim driver/main.c

vriskeis th grammh static long perma_mmap_buf_size
kai analoga me to megethos pou thes xrisimopoieis to antistoixo define
pou uparxei apo panw.
Gia na ginei apply to kainourgio megethos pou tha desmefsei h fmap
prepei na kaneis rebuild thn fmap.

cd driver
make clean;make 

Gia na fortwseis thn fmap arkei na trexeis to arxeio
00_load-it-sith6.sh 
prwta omws prepei na valeis to device pou tha apothikevei ta dedomena
h fmap.Auto to kaneis
me to na allaxeis th metavlhth DEVICE pou einai sth prwth grammh tou
arxeiou 00_load-it-sith6.sh.
Otan fortwseis th dmap tha emfanistei to device /dev/dmap/dmap1 opou
xrisimopoieis gia na kaneis ta peiramata sou.
Gia na kaneis unload thn fmap arkei na trexeis to 00_remove-it.sh to
opoio de paizei mallon auth ti stigmi.
